The '''Athega system''' contained the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nkllon/Legends|Nkllon]]. Because of the system's extremely hot star, the system was off-limits until [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], backed by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], led an [[Nomad City|expedition]] to Nkllon to mine its mineral rich surface.

A [[Battle near Athega|space battle]] between the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] took place in the system during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="XWvTF">''[[Star Wars: X-Wing vs. TIE Fighter]]''</ref>

